g src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sa5sWmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSa5sWmr.jpg&h=2e6a418c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2skMss7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2skMss7.jpg&h=077c238a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門<br />\n<br />\n德國聯署要人！倒數四日！但得一萬人咋！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798520</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最新日程表出咗啦 除夕元旦都有行動呀<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/1798785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1798785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4aea6462b1123ed0ba50fae60ea1bafb23b186af","tid":1798461,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T01:17:39.000Z","msg":"係巴基斯坦同柬埔寨起深水港<br />\n又想係泰國起運河<br />\n仲想係新加坡對出起個城市出黎<br />\n馬六甲至於支那<br />\n就等於達達尼爾海峽至於沙俄<br />\n畀你起到都冇撚用啦<br />\n你啲黑煙艦過到馬六甲入到印度洋新港口駐紮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條運河你投射到軍力去&ldquo;保護&rdquo;咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係美軍基地隔離既新港口城市會有運行咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出錢出力起好啲嘢咪又係一句唔該畀人擸埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據加速主義<br />\n我地應該鼓勵支那勇敢走出去<br />\n最好成個國家投入去一帶一路<br />\n就好似葡京啲賭仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}